metadata.synopsis: Squirrely, quick-breathing, animalian worg (wolf-like creature) stands guard at a checkpoint with its masters.

0.speaker: Klaw
0.text: Wearin' me muck. Muck on ya. Good muck.
0.context: NodeContext: Sniffing and snuffling at the shit on your face. Spoken quickly, primal.

1.speaker: Klaw
1.text: Rip ya. Rip ya fer yer giblets. Got thick giblets. Want 'em.
1.context: NodeContext: Slavering worg, hungry, vicious. Spoken quickly.
